messageBody:
Dear fellow,
I am a student doing my final assignment at my colleagues in Indonesia.
I am researching Xtreme Programming Development using Java.
I've read some of the XP book such as Agile Java, TDD Programming, and SAMS
TYS XP in 21 days.
Currently,
I am searching for a concise study case as my XP project, but as a lone
programmer.
Would you kind pinpoint me to an internet reference for this study case
matter? Or, maybe you have a concise study case for me to work with.
I am eager to wait for your answer.
Thanks in advance for your reply.
Cheers...,
Swayz
